text: Aigle is a district of the canton of Vaud, Switzerland. It contains the following municipalities: * Aigle * Bex * Chessel * Corbeyrier * Gryon * Lavey-Morcles * Leysin * Noville * Ollon * Ormont-Dessous * Ormont-Dessus * Rennaz * Roche * Villeneuve * Yvorne Category:Aigle (district)
